video.name: Alaska in 8K 60p HDR  (Dolby Vision)
video.description: Explore Juneau, Alaska with us as we navigate through an Alaskan summer.We visited the Tracy Arm Fjord, Mendenhall Glacier, Pack Creek bears, Hoonah, and some beautiful Juneau icebergs. To view at 8K 60P you'll need to use Chrome.
